  "body": "This PR adds `warning` on the legacy context APIs when it's under StrictMode. Specifically, just to make sure, the `if` statement looks like this:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nif (\r\n  typeof instance.getChildContext === 'function' ||\r\n  (fiber.tag === ClassComponent && fiber.type.contextTypes != null) ||\r\n  (fiber.tag === ClassComponent && fiber.type.childContextTypes != null)\r\n)\r\n``` \r\n\r\nFeel free to leave comments. \r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13282699/40259374-a823d4ca-5aaa-11e8-9fcb-b46ee87d5ced.png)",
